  "description": "Luca leads Ecosystem Development at OpenZeppelin, focusing on expanding OpenZeppelin Contracts for Solidity and new execution environments. His first full-time job, while at university, was building products on Ethereum. Passionate about the Ethereum community, Luca was part of the organizing team for the first Devconnect in Amsterdam. He now organizes Latin America’s largest Ethereum hackathons as a Co-Founder of ETHSamba and founded Bamba, a physical hub for crypto projects in Rio de Janeiro.",
